import { Box, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material' import React from 'react' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import styles from "./style.module.scss" import { ADD_TO_CART_SECTION, CHOICE, TODO_SECTION } from '../../../utils/constants' const HomeComponent = () => { const navigate = useNavigate() return (
{CHOICE} <> { navigate("/todo") }} className={styles.boxes}> {TODO_SECTION} { navigate("/cart") }} className={styles.boxes}> {ADD_TO_CART_SECTION}
) } export default HomeComponent
